Package grafioschtrader.algo.strategy.model

Class StrategyClassBindingDefinition

java.lang.Object
grafioschtrader.algo.strategy.model.StrategyClassBindingDefinition
public class StrategyClassBindingDefinition extends Object
The class for a particular strategy can be different at different levels. The user will make his settings via these classes. It may also make sense to have a strategy only at the top level or, for example, on a security.
